        public OntologyMetaData(java.lang.String id,
                        java.lang.String prefix,
                        java.lang.String namespace,
                        java.util.HashSet<java.lang.String> dependancy)
                 throws OntologyMetaDataException
        OntologyMetaData constructor linked to the JSON parser (jackson api) Notice that the ontology IRI is calculated by removing last character of prefix String
        Parameters:
        id - : String - ontology id
        prefix - : String - ontology prefix (common part of URI for all elements into the ontology)
        namespace - : String - namespace used for the ontology whithin the current ontology as well as for dependancies management
        dependancy - : HashSet - list of ontology dependancies (by id)
        Throws:
        OntologyMetaDataException - (if id is empty or null or OntologyPrefix object creation fails)
